The strongest **control-law** proof is Meta²’s actual gate enforcement plus runnable validation surfaces:
- `/Users/jobs/Desktop/Desktop(archive)/github/meta2-engine/engine/src/main.rs` exposes `/run`, `/validate`, `/validate_golden`, `/meta/run`, `/nstar/run`
- `/Users/jobs/Desktop/Desktop(archive)/github/meta2-engine/engine/src/engine/validate.rs` runs suites over easy/hard/impossible/adaptive tasks
- `/Users/jobs/Desktop/Desktop(archive)/github/meta2-engine/engine/src/engine/golden.rs` validates golden trace structure and has a real test for `wolfram_unity`

The caveat: the golden validator mainly checks **bit validity/shape**, not deep behavioral truth.

